entry.title: First international concert
entry.content: We are stoked to announce that we will perform at the Metal Magic Warmup Party in Fredericia, Denmark on Walpurgis Night (April 30). Our first gig abroad!

entry.title: Debut LP released today!
entry.content: Our debut album Katakombernas Kakofoni is finally out TODAY! Order from Jawbreaker Records.

entry.title: Tyrannosatan Online
entry.content: Website launched today. "Social" media will be closed down soon. Follow us here or with RSS for ill omens and other prophetic visions of the future.
